articles.author: Ian Livingston
articles.title: Cyclone Alfred heading toward Brisbane and eastern Australia for rare landfall - The Washington Post
articles.description: Alfred is forecast to make landfall near Brisbane, the capital of Queensland and Australia’s third largest city.
articles.content: Tropical Cyclone Alfred is approaching Australias east coast and could hit land in about a day. Ahead of the expected impact on one of the continents most populated and well-known stretches of shorel… [+4615 chars]
